DESCRIPTION:Nephrology Grand Rounds are the primary teaching conference of
  the Division of\nNephrology. Both clinical and basic science topics pert
 inent to nephrology are\npresented at this conference. Each fellow\, guid
 ed by a faculty-mentor\, will\npresent once a year. Speakers from outside
  the Division of Nephrology and Duke\nUniversity will also be incorporate
 d into the conference schedule.
DURATION:PT1H
